content: {"name": "Community Health Van Menino YMCA", "alternate_name": "", "description": "To better support individuals who live and work in communities hardest hit by COVID-19, Brigham and Women\u2019s Faulkner Hospital has launched a community health van offering a variety of services including: \u2022 Masks and hand sanitizer \u2022 Blood pressure checks \u2022 Food bags (limited) \u2022 Connection to services (housing, food, utilities, legal, behavioral health, safety,\nhealthcare access) \u2022 Other personal care items as available\nThey charge for some of their food items", "email": "", "url": "http://ymcaboston.org/menino", "status": "active", "address": {"address_1": "1137 River Street", "address_2": null, "city": "Hyde Park", "state_province": "MA", "postal_code": "02136", "country": "US"}, "location": {"latitude": 42.2571744, "longitude": -71.1204395}, "phones": [{"number": "(617) 361-2300", "type": "voice"}], "regular_schedule": [{"weekday": "Thursday", "opens_at": "20:00", "closes_at": "22:30"}]}
